testCase.name: UsersCacheVerifierService should be able to list a cached role
UsersCacheVerifierService should be able to list all cached roles
ListRolesByNameService should be able to list a role with a valid name
ListRolesByNameService should not be able to list a role with a invalid name
ListRoleService should be able to list a role with a valid id
ListRoleService should not be able to list a role with a invalid id
ListAllRolesService should be able to list all roles
ListAddressService should be able to list a valid address
ListAddressService should not be able to delete a address with invalid user_id
ListAddressService should not be able to delete a address with invalid address_id
DeleteAddressService should be able to delete a valid address
DeleteAddressService should not be able to delete a address with invalid user_id
DeleteAddressService should not be able to delete a address with invalid address_id
UsersCacheVerifierService should be able to list a cached user
ListAllAddressesService should be able to list all addresses of a valid user_id
ListAllAddressesService should not be able to list all addresses of a invalid user_id
ListUserService should be able to list a user with a valid id
ListUserService should not be able to list a user with a invalid id
CreateUserService should be able create a user with a valid credentials
CreateUserService should not be able create a user with same email
CreateUserService should not be able create a user with same document number
CreateUserService should be able create a user without informing the role
AddressesCacheVerifierService should be able to list a cached address
AddressesCacheVerifierService should be able to list many cached address
UpdateUserService should be able update a user with a valid id
UpdateUserService should not be able update a user with a invalid id
UpdateUserService should not be able update a user email to a already existing one
CreateAddressService should be able to create a address with a valid credentials
CreateAddressService should change the main_address_id of the user to the new address
CreateAddressService should not be able to create a address with a invalid user id
UpdateAddressService should be able to update a valid address
UpdateAddressService should not be able to update a address with invalid user_id
UpdateAddressService should not be able to update a address with invalid address_id
